{
  "analysis": "Script ran without apparent errors and produced archive. However we need to verify that exclusions and processing worked correctly. Let's examine the archive contents and check that excluded files are not present, line endings normalized, permissions set, timestamps set, etc.\n\nFirst, list contents of archive with tar -tvf to see metadata.",
  "plan": "Run tar -tvf on the archive, checking for excluded patterns and timestamps. Also extract a few files to verify line endings and permissions. We'll also compute sha256 of archive to ensure deterministic with same SOURCE_DATE_EPOCH.\n\nWe'll also need to ensure that the archive is deterministic across runs: run again with same epoch and compare sha256.\n\nLet's proceed.",
